data.title: World War II Antiques & Collectibles
data.text:
Disclaimer

This site is intented for the sale of military antiques from the First and Second World War. It is dedicated to collectors, musea and other persons with an historical interest in this period.

The items for sale on this site are sold for historical or research purposes only.

Customers of MilitariaRelics are obligated to use all articles accordingly.

We would like to make clear that we do not support the beliefs or actions of the Third Reich or any other right wing or fascist organisation, current or past.

If you have any other intention, please do not continue.
